# Next.js SSR-first conventions

- Prefer Server Components and SSR by default; only add `"use client"` when interaction or browser-only APIs are required.
- Co-locate server actions with routes where appropriate; keep them type-safe.
- Consider streaming and Suspense for progressive rendering.
- Use path alias `@/*` for imports (see [`tsconfig.json`](mdc:tsconfig.json)).

